==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} a crab. Applied to cancerous tumors because the enlarged veins ressembled the legs of a crab.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A disease where the cells of various body tissues begin uncontrolled (and often rapid) proliferation.

